  "description": "<p>1. JOB DESCRIPTION</p><p><strong>Job Title</strong></p><p>ACCOUNTS ASSISTANT</p><p><strong>Occupation</strong></p><p>ACCOUNTS ASSISTANT</p><p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Accounts receivables (Including billing & credit control)</li><li>Accounts Payable (Claims）</li><li>Generation of AR reports (AR aging, sales listing) and reconciliations</li><li>Assist in other tasks that may be assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Word & Excel.</li><li>Minimum 2year experience</li><li>Minimum Diploma in Accountancy</li><li>Able to multi-task and possess a positive attitude</li><li>Able to work under minimal supervision</li><li>Tight deadlines</li><li>Willing to perform data entry, meticulous and detailed</li><li>Able to communicate in Mandrain.</li></ul><p>5.5days work week.</p><p>Singaporean / Singapore PR only. <br />Preferably staying in Woodlands/Sembawang.</p>",
